7123;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1227123";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Daghda";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1196";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Cocoa";s:4:"text";s:235:"I am genuinely sorry. I&#039;m the kind of person who can take that kind of talk because that&#039;s kind of how Australian sociology is. You insult each other with colourful words and it&#039;s funny. So that doesn&#039;t help either.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1422225693";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#933aaa";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14222256961";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#4bc7f0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1227125;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1227125";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Daghda";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1196";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Cocoa";s:4:"text";s:191:"I guess the difference really is that I have a very specific view on... expression, I guess. As I said on a facebook post recently regarding why the word &#039;cis&#039; is really aggressive:";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1422225735";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#933aaa";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14222257377";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#4bc7f0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1227130;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1227130";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Daghda";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1196";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Cocoa";s:4:"text";s:326:"&quot;I believe that the vocal part of the LGBT+ community is a large part of the reason that we as a people face the ostracism that we face. It&#039;s the exagguration, the weirdness, the open insanity that some (but not all people) express that is a REASON that we are seen as lesser, and broken, and weird, and undesirable.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1422225826";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#933aaa";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14222258288";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#4bc7f0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1227131;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1227131";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"4167";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Cocoa";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"474";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Daghda";s:4:"text";s:194:"Well I think the word cis is stupid, I hate that people have abused LGBT to the point that the word cis even exists, you were just the last person I would expect to call me something like that. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1422225841";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#852b00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14222258417";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c8652c";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1227132;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1227132";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:6:"Daghda";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1196";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Cocoa";s:4:"text";s:157:"Be who you want to be. But be so yourself. You don&#039;t have to tell everyone and make the biggest deal about it, there&#039;s just more to life than this.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1422225853";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#933aaa";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14222258562";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#4bc7f0";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1227148;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1227148";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"4167";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Cocoa";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"474";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:6:"Daghda";s:4:"text";s:240:"I guess it&#039;s okay, it just feels so meh with a bunch of excused tied to it. My friend stole my hat and threw it in the trash, then actually expected me to believe he did it because of pain meds. Really? We had /just/ had an arguement. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1422226034";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#852b00";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14222260347";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#c8652c";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1227150;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1227150";s:12:"chat_ro